reviewText:
This tape is really a westside barbell info commercial displaying several westside products.
The reverse hyper, a bench, a rack, squatting belt(with chains), and tapes are briefly discussed
in the approx. 15 minute tape. I was expecting a great deal more in terms of the reverse hyper
discussion, but when this tape was made they only had the original reverse hyper. Since it was
basically an info commercial, I would have loved to see an hour or more displaying as many of the
products sold by westside as possible.
